# AlternativeDistributionPackage.Relationships

**Object**

The data structure that represents the relationships of an alternative distribution package resource.

## Declaration

```swift
object AlternativeDistributionPackage.Relationships
```

## Discussion

For more information on the object that owns these relationships, see [doc://com.apple.appstoreconnectapi/documentation/AppStoreConnectAPI/AlternativeDistributionPackage].

## Objects

- **AlternativeDistributionPackage.Relationships.Versions**: The data structure that represents the versions for the relationships of an alternative distribution package resource.
